<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="G" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Glib1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Glib,</orth> adj. smooth, slippery: <cit><quote>so g. of tongue,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 4.5.58" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. IV, 5, 58</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>g. and slippery creatures,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tim 1.1.53" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. I, 1, 53</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>that g. and oily art to speak and purpose not,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lr 1.1.227" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. I, 1, 227</bibl></cit>.
